OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy this morning,
OL,6,Fscattered showers or thundery
OL,7,Fdownpours bring the potential for
OL,8,Ffrequent lightning, although not
OL,9,Feverywhere will see these. Drier and
OL,10,Fsunnier this afternoon, becoming
OL,11,Fwidely warm or very warm, although
OL,12,Fstaying cooler and breezier at the
OL,13,Fcoast.
OL,14,
OL,15,CTonight:FDry and sunny this evening
OL,16,Fand remaining largely dry overnight.
OL,17,FCloud tending to increase in many
OL,18,Fareas by morning, perhaps bringing a
OL,19,Ffew spots of light rain across the
OL,20,FPennines.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
