OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA dry day with plenty of
OL,6,Fsunshine, though perhaps the chance
OL,7,Ffor a little light rain on western
OL,8,Fhills at first. Feeling fresher
OL,9,Finland, but warmer at the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry,
OL,12,Flargely sunny and warm or very warm on
OL,13,FSaturday. Trending cooler and more
OL,14,Fchangeable from Sunday. An increased
OL,15,Fchance of rain, but still some fine,
OL,16,Fwarm weather at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
